OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder launches new bid to clear his
OL,5,Cname
OL,7,FA man who served 36 years behind bars
OL,8,Ffor the savage murder of a betting
OL,9,Fshop manager has told ITV Granada
OL,10,FReports he's innocent of the crime and
OL,11,Fwill never give up fighting to clear
OL,12,Fhis name.
OL,14,FRay Gilbert, 66, was convicted of
OL,15,Fstabbing John Suffield Junior 19 times
OL,16,Fat the Coral Racing Shop, on Lodge
OL,17,FLane, Toxteth, in what was believed to
OL,18,Fhave been a botched robbery in 1981.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
