OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder launches new bid to clear his
OL,5,Cname
OL,7,FMr Gilbert, who was aged 22 at the
OL,8,Ftime of his arrest, initially admitted
OL,9,Fthe crime - but says he was coerced
OL,10,Fand threatened into confessing during
OL,11,F48-hours of police questioning staged
OL,12,Fwithout legal representation or an
OL,13,Fappropriate adult.
OL,15,FHe has maintained his innocence even
OL,16,Fthough it cost him an extra 20 years
OL,17,Fin prison because of his refusal to
OL,18,Fconfess to a Parole Board.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
