OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder launches new bid to clear his
OL,5,Cname
OL,7,FMr Gilbert was eventually released in
OL,8,F2016 and has kept up the flight to
OL,9,Fclear his name.
OL,11,FCo-defendant, John Karmara, had his
OL,12,Fconviction overturned in 2001, when an
OL,13,Fappeal court found hundreds of witness
OL,14,Fstatements were kept from the defence
OL,15,Fteam.
OL,17,FBut because Mr Gilbert initially
OL,18,Fconfessed to the killing, he has never
OL,19,Fhad the chance to appeal his own
OL,20,Fconviction.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
