OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder launches new bid to clear his
OL,5,Cname
OL,7,FNow an independent investigator is
OL,8,Fhelping him with a fresh bid to the
OL,9,FCriminal Cases Review Commission
OL,10,F(CCRC).
OL,12,FMr Gilbert said: "I want to prove my
OL,13,Finnocence. I want to be able to hold
OL,14,Fmy head up high.
OL,16,F"It's nothing to do about money, I
OL,17,Fjust want my innocence proven.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
