OL,7,F"But this time, I'm offering a brand
OL,8,Fnew argument."
OL,10,FThe team also say that - just like
OL,11,FJohn Karmara's case - there is
OL,12,Fdocumentary evidence which proves Mr
OL,13,FGilbert could not have committed the
OL,14,Fcrime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
