OL,5,Cname
OL,7,FHayley Wood, a Miscarriage of Justice
OL,8,FAdvocate, who is also working on Ray's
OL,9,Fbehalf said: "It's within these
OL,10,Fdocuments we have found certain
OL,11,Finformation that suggests that Ray was
OL,12,Fcertainly not in the place that he was
OL,13,Fforced to confess to where he was.
OL,15,F"On the run up to Ray's arrest - eye
OL,16,Fwitnesses described the attackers, or
OL,17,Fthose trying to gain access to the
OL,18,Fbuilding as being white men, and then
OL,19,Fonce Ray was arrested, witnesses were
OL,20,Fthen saying they were mixed race.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
