OL,5,Cname
OL,7,F"Ray and John Kamara weren't even
OL,8,Ftogether at the time of the murder and
OL,9,Fthere's no evidence to link them to
OL,10,Fthis crime."
OL,12,FShe added: "I really hope this time
OL,13,Fthe CCRC will listen and that they'll
OL,14,Fat least do a forensic review of any
OL,15,Fremaining samples.
OL,17,F"If Ray's case does get referred to
OL,18,Fthe court of appeal - then this could
OL,19,Fbe one of the longest miscarriages of
OL,20,Fjustice known in the UK."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
