OL,7,FA Merseyside Police spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"The Criminal Case Review Commission
OL,9,F(CCRC) has previously reviewed the
OL,10,Fconviction of Raymond Gilbert
OL,11,Ffollowing the murder of John Suffield
OL,12,Fand the grounds for appeal were
OL,13,Fdismissed and the conviction deemed
OL,14,Fsafe.
OL,16,F"Merseyside Police are aware that a
OL,17,Ffurther application has been made to
OL,18,Fthe CCRC, but are unaware of any
OL,19,Ffurther detail."
